Feature: Product Expert Smoke Tests

    Background:
    Given I go to the Product Expert URL
    
    Scenario: User closes welcome page
    When I click to close the welcome page   
    Then the motivation page is displayed 
    
    Scenario: User opens burger menu
    When I click to close the welcome page 
    When I click to open the burger menu
    Then the burger menu is expanded
    
    When I click to close the burger menu
    Then the burger menu is collasped
    
    When I click the search icon
    Then an empty search page is displayed
    
    When I click the basket icon
    Then an empty basket page is displayed 
    
    When I click the back arrow
    Then I am taken back to the empty search page
